thread.title: fleanote

author: fleanote
title: fleanote
text: Great experience and have been using Frames Direct for Years. My only complaint is that within the description and images of various frames, there is no indication of where the frame is manufactured. For some, that is immaterial. For others, like me, I trust Italian made frames, not so much for those made in China, so I need to see that when making purchases.
